Bank of Japan-originated material
=================================

The fixed database identifiers and English and Japanese database names used by
boj_databases() are based on the Bank of Japan's API manuals dated February 18,
2026:

  https://www.stat-search.boj.or.jp/info/api_manual_en.pdf
  https://www.stat-search.boj.or.jp/info/api_manual.pdf

The prescribed English and Japanese credit text is reproduced from the Bank of
Japan's notices:

  https://www.stat-search.boj.or.jp/info/api_notice_en.pdf
  https://www.stat-search.boj.or.jp/info/api_notice.pdf

Test fixtures reproduce selected API field names and illustrative series
metadata to validate response parsing. Their numerical observations are
synthetic and are not Bank of Japan observations.

These Bank of Japan-originated identifiers, names, and credit text are not
relicensed under the bojapi MIT license. Any rights in them remain with their
respective rightsholders, and their use remains subject to the current
applicable terms. No actual Bank of Japan time-series observations or API
manuals are bundled in the source or installed package.
